title: Ejaculation
plot: As Andrew falls under the spell of the randy Hormone Monster, his buddy Nick becomes obsessed with the lack of changes in his own body.

title: Everybody Bleeds
plot: A field trip goes from awkward to mortifying as Jessi navigates the demands of coupledom and gets her first period -- inside the Statue of Liberty.

title: Am I Gay?
plot: A trailer for a new movie starring The Rock leaves Andrew questioning his sexuality. Jessi and Nick's budding romance turns ugly fast.

title: Sleepover: A Harrowing Ordeal of Emotional Brutality
plot: While the boys head to Jay's for a testosterone-fueled sleepover, Jessi throws a party of her own and gets caught up in mean-girl drama.
episode_title: Sleepover: A Harrowing Ordeal of Emotional Brutality

title: Girls Are Horny Too
plot: A steamy novel making the rounds at school inspires Jessi to explore her own sexuality -- and leaves the boys totally confused about what girls want.

title: Pillow Talk
plot: Nick drags Andrew into the city to visit an old camp crush, but the day doesn't go as planned. Jay embarks on an emotional journey with his pillow.

title: Requiem for a Wet Dream
plot: Andrew struggles to keep the Hormone Monster in check as he works with Missy on a science fair project. Jessi and Matthew have fun at Jay's expense.

title: The Head Push
plot: When Leah hosts a party for the high school drama crowd, Nick wrestles with a romantic dilemma, and Andrew and Missy witness a disturbing scene.

title: I Survived Jessi's Bat Mitzvah
plot: Family blowups, secret liaisons and an unflattering dress make Jessi's bat mitzvah a night to remember.

title: The Pornscape
plot: Andrew tries to drown his sorrows in a sea of porn, only to become hopelessly addicted. Coach Steve becomes a suspect in a murder spree.

title: Am I Normal?
plot: Andrew struggles to blend in after a growth spurt, Nick worries his hormones are out of whack, and Jessi and Jay get a taste of the teen runaway life.

title: What Is It About Boobs?
plot: A classmate's booming bosom sends the boys into a rapture - and leaves the girls with a raging sense of insecurity. Coach Steve drops a bombshell.

title: The Shame Wizard
plot: As Nick tries to figure out whether he has a shot with Gina, a mortifying encounter with Leah sends Andrew into a spiral of shame.

title: Steve the Virgin
plot: Coach Steve finally gets his chance to do sex on a lady, Nick and Andrew go on a double date, and Jessi's rebellious streak leads to big trouble.

title: The Planned Parenthood Show
plot: An argument in sex ed class turns into a skit-tastic journey through the worlds of Planned Parenthood, contraceptives and STDs.

title: Drug Buddies
plot: Jess and Nick dip into her dad's stash of edibles, with mind-bending results. Andrew searches for the right moment to break up with Lola.

title: Guy Town
plot: While helping Greg move into a seedy bachelor complex, the boys and their dads debate what women want - and what it means to be a man.

title: Dark Side of the Boob
plot: A school sleepover turns messy as Nick dishes on a makeout session and the Shame Wizard works his miserable magic on the whole class.

title: Smooch or Share
plot: Nick tries to lighten the mood at the sleepover with a new twist on Truth or Dare. The Shame Wizard meets his match. Jessi vows to change her ways.

title: The Department of Puberty
plot: After traveling through a magic portal to puberty headquarters, Nick seeks out a new Hormone Monster and Jessi bonds with the Depression Kitty.
